OL,3,CSir Paul McCartney at London's
OL,4,CRoundhouse for special live event
OL,6,FSir Paul McCartney will host a special
OL,7,Flive event to discuss the journey
OL,8,Fbehind his latest album, The Boys Of
OL,9,FDungeon Lane.
OL,11,FThe Beatles star will reflect on how
OL,12,Fhe made the album at 'The Boys Of
OL,13,FDungeon Lane' In Conversation with
OL,14,FPaul McCartney Roundhouse live event
OL,15,Fon June 10.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/5
