OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1781093477
OL,3,CSir Paul McCartney at London's
OL,4,CRoundhouse for special live event
OL,6,FThe evening will offer fans the chance
OL,7,Fto get a first-hand perspective on how
OL,8,Fthe record came to life and hear
OL,9,Fstories from Sir Paul from his first
OL,10,Fmeeting with producer Andrew Watt in
OL,11,F2021 through to the recording process,
OL,12,Fsongwriting and the album's release
OL,13,Flast week.
OL,15,FIt will also include reflections from
OL,16,FSir Paul on duetting with Beatles
OL,17,Fdrummer Sir Ringo Starr for the first
OL,18,Ftime.
OL,20,FTickets for the live event go on sale
OL,21,Fon Wednesday morning.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/5
