OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1781093477
OL,3,CSir Paul McCartney at London's
OL,4,CRoundhouse for special live event
OL,6,FThe album is Sir Paul's first record
OL,7,Fin five years and named after a place
OL,8,Fclose to his childhood home in
OL,9,FForthlin Road in the Liverpool suburb
OL,10,Fof Speke.
OL,12,FReleased last week, the 14-track
OL,13,Frecord recounts a collection of
OL,14,Fmemories from the singer's formative
OL,15,Fyears in Liverpool including his early
OL,16,Fadventures with his late bandmates
OL,17,FGeorge Harrison and John Lennon, prior
OL,18,Fto their Beatles fame.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/5
