OL,3,CSir Paul McCartney at London's
OL,4,CRoundhouse for special live event
OL,6,FFormed in 1960, The Beatles was made
OL,7,Fup of Sir Paul, Lennon, Harrison and
OL,8,FSir Ringo and went on to become the
OL,9,Fbest-selling musical act of all time
OL,10,Fand one of the most influential groups
OL,11,Fin the world.
OL,13,FThe band achieved 16 UK number one
OL,14,Falbums and 18 UK number one singles
OL,15,Fincluding Help!, Hey Jude and She
OL,16,FLoves You until their split in 1970.
OL,18,FSir Paul launched his solo career and
OL,19,Freleased his debut solo album,
OL,20,FMcCartney.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/5
